    Build composable event pipeline servers with minimal effort.


    =======================
    wishbone.decode.msgpack
    =======================

    Version: 1.0.0

    Decodes MSGPack data into Python objects.
    -----------------------------------------


        Decodes the payload or complete events from MSGPack format.

        Parameters:

            - complete(bool)(False)
               |  When True encodes the complete event.  If False only
               |  encodes the data part.

        Queues:

            - inbox
               |  Incoming messages

            - outbox
               |  Outgoing messges
info.name: wishbone_decode_msgpack
info.summary: A Wishbone decode module to convert MSGPack data into Python dict data structures.
